{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/issues/160/comments/36693280.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim/issues/160#comment-36693280"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/issues/160.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 160, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{c41021d9-0217-4628-999d-7f8d82f98dcb}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "srcsim", "full_name": "osrf/srcsim", "uuid": "{c41021d9-0217-4628-999d-7f8d82f98dcb}"}, "title": "world frame not accessible on field in local setup"}, "content": {"raw": "In my experience, we had to change the ROS_MASTER_URI and ROS_IP before launching gazebo to use the docker interface IP instead of the one specified in the installation instructions #!/osrf/srcsim/wiki/system_setup\n\nWe have this in our bashrc \n\n\n```\n#!bash\nexport ROS_MASTER_URI=http://`hostname -i`:11311\nexport ROS_IP=`hostname -i`\n\n\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In my experience, we had to change the ROS_MASTER_URI and ROS_IP before launching gazebo to use the docker interface IP instead of the one specified in the installation instructions <a href=\"#!/osrf/srcsim/wiki/system_setup\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#!/osrf/srcsim/wiki/system_setup</a></p>\n<p>We have this in our bashrc </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-bash\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nb\">export</span> <span class=\"nv\">ROS_MASTER_URI</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>http://<span class=\"sb\">`</span>hostname -i<span class=\"sb\">`</span>:11311\n<span class=\"nb\">export</span> <span class=\"nv\">ROS_IP</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>hostname -i<span class=\"sb\">`</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-05-10T10:28:35.150189+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "V\u00edctor L\u00f3pez", "uuid": "{45ae86e9-e602-472d-b978-9915cf7f0b94}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B45ae86e9-e602-472d-b978-9915cf7f0b94%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B45ae86e9-e602-472d-b978-9915cf7f0b94%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/441581ed0d88303764d0971c84961d4dd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsVL-3.png"}}, "nickname": "Victor Lopez", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:be4eaa58-1e6c-457d-b177-531b37dc6861"}, "updated_on": "2017-05-10T10:28:43.000085+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 36693280}